------------------------------------------------------------
* Removed traces of old ReactNow name
* Tidied up starter kit fonts

0.1.2
------------------------------------------------------------
* Really fixed the logo (hopefully)

0.1.1
------------------------------------------------------------
* Image fix for ReactQL logo

0.1.0
------------------------------------------------------------
* Initial release.  Pre-alpha -- don't use yet, not finished!
